There are two methods for viewing app container metrics on PAS deployments:

Loggregator Firehose: No configuration required. Emitted as text payload with format up to developer. (https://github.com/cloudfoundry/loggregator-api/blob/master/README.md). 
Note: The Firehose does not emit logs for service instances. To view service instance logs, use the syslog drain method. 
Syslog: Requires configuration of Syslog Adapter Drain (https://docs.cloudfoundry.org/devguide/services/log-management.html#step2). Emitted as Syslog RFC 5426.

